stateDiagram-v2
    [*] --> initialize_session
    initialize_session --> assign_roles: Session created
    assign_roles --> dispatch_turn: Roles assigned to agents
    dispatch_turn --> collect_results: Execution token issued
    collect_results --> resolve_conflicts: Agent completed turn
    resolve_conflicts --> broadcast_updates: Conflicts resolved
    broadcast_updates --> dispatch_turn: Next turn (iterative)
    broadcast_updates --> complete_session: Final state update
    complete_session --> [*]
    
    note right of initialize_session
        Create Collab object
        Set mode (round_robin/broadcast/orchestrated)
        Bind to Context
    end note
    
    note right of assign_roles
        Map agents to roles
        Populate Collab.participants[]
        Validate Role capabilities
    end note
    
    note right of dispatch_turn
        Issue execution_token to role
        Emit MAPTurnDispatched event
        Agent begins execution
    end note
    
    note right of collect_results
        Agent signals completion
        Emit MAPTurnCompleted event
        Collect execution outcome
    end note
    
    note right of resolve_conflicts
        Check for concurrent modifications
        Emit MAPConflictDetected (if any)
        Emit MAPConflictResolved
    end note
    
    note right of broadcast_updates
        Sync state across participants
        Emit MAPBroadcastSent
        Prepare for next turn or completion
    end note
